府.definition: seat of government; government repository (archive); official residence; mansion; presidential palace; (honorific) Your home; prefecture (from Tang to Qing times)

府城.definition: capital of 府 prefecture (from Tang to Qing times); prefectural seat

府治.definition: seat of prefectural government (from Tang to Qing times)

府試.definition: prefectural exam, the 2nd of the three entry-level exams in the imperial examination system of Ming and Qing dynasties

府谷.definition: Fugu County in Yulin 榆林[Yu2 lin2], Shaanxi

府谷縣.definition: Fugu County in Yulin 榆林[Yu2 lin2], Shaanxi
